title: Bella Hadid looks chic in a Nineties grey hoodie in London | Daily Mail Online
text: Buy now Meanwhile, Bella - who is currently in London for Fashion Week - flaunted her penchant for fast and greasy food with Kendall Jenner on Sunday. The two were pictured eating lemon chicken wings sitting on the floor at a photo shoot in an image posted to Instagram by Bella. The model, 20, and the reality star turned model, 21, shared a snap from the set of their photoshoot during London Fashion Week. Stylish: Letting her 'ice studios' sweatshirt do all the talking, she accessorised simply with purple-tinted cat-eye shades Ready for her close up: Styling her raven tresses in a sleek side-parting, she kept her make-up minimal to showcase her striking feature But first, let me take a selfie: She smouldered in a pouty Instagram snap The American model posted a snap of the duo looking chic in flat caps, denim and lounge wear after being photographed by Renell Medrano on Sunday. Sharing the mouth-watering remnants of their chicken wing and garlic bread feast, she captioned the picture: 'nandos lemon wings (sic).' The younger Hadid sister has been giving followers major food envy, taking to Instagram on Wednesday to show her 'between show snack' of 10 Mcdonald's chicken nuggets during New York Fashion Week. Chowing down: Bella Hadid and Kendall Jenner gnawed on lemon chicken wings in this Instagram snap shared during a break in a photo shoot in London Sunday night Share or comment on this article Most watched News videos
